# Zero Regression Rule

- Keep visual output and behavior 100% unchanged unless the user explicitly asks for a functional change.
- Prefer structural refactors (module boundaries, comments, naming clarity) over logic rewrites.
- Preserve initialization order and event wiring order in `js/app.js`.
- For CSS cleanup, keep selector specificity and effective cascade unchanged.
